data.description: Remarkable opportunity! This home features 4 bedroom, 2 baths, plus an office with french doors. Well-designed for comfortable and flexible living, for working, entertaining and includes a spacious garage with utility sink. An open floor plan welcomes you to the kitchen/family room combo featuring high ceilings, overlooking the spacious backyard. The kitchen features a gas range, ample 42” cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and a walk-in pantry.  This home has easy access to 301, Crosstown Expressway and I-75, and is close to the highly rated hospitals, the VA clinic, Publix, and lots of restaurants and shopping. Call today to schedule a showing.
